Lost Creek neighborhood, just across Rt 30, northwest corner of Arlington TX. We're right between Dallas and Ft. Worth, within 15 minutes of DFW. A  right fine location in a friendly part of town. We ask only for quiet after 10 PM.

Public Transportation is Uber, Lyft, and other taxi companies. Some of the venues offer shuttles. For example, on game day Boston's Gourmet Pizza (maybe a mile from here) runs a shuttle to either stadium

Coffee and espresso makers, rice/slow/pressure cookers, blender, toaster, refrigerator, stove, and dishwasher. Place settings, linens and towels for 8. There's quite a few kitchen accessories available, just open the cupboards and take a look.

Description:
Welcome to "Lola"!

My place is a 2 bedroom 1.5 bath duplex in the heart of DFW. It's a 2-story 1050sqft with both bedrooms being upstairs. 

There are two queen mattress and the third bed is a queen fold away memory foam mattress.

PETS: Must be pre-approved. $40 per pet (Additional pets charged after booking)

Only a couple miles away from the Cowboys/Ranger Stadium, Six Flags, Arlington Convention Center or UTA. 

City of Arlington implemented:  
No gatherings; 6 person max

You have the whole place to yourself! I am a call away if you need anything during your stay. I take pride in making sure the place is clean for each and every guest. I do understand privacy, so I will give your space. I just ask you leave the place the same way you found it. Mi Casa es tu casa!

Late Check-ins: You can access my place by yourself anytime after 4pm so no worries on late flights, take your time!
 
Please feel free to reach out with any questions! :)

You will have the "B" side of my duplex. This includes 2 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, kitchen, Living room, Patio, 1 Spot of the covered parking. It's about 1050 square feet.

I will be able to assist in any way I can! If you give me the opportunity,  I will always try to work offer recommendations and make sure you have the most comfortable stay possible! :)

The Neighborhood is quiet and the duplex sits on the end of a col-de-sac. I lived there myself prior to hosting it on Airbnb. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, business travelers, and families looking for a home away from home with access to all that DFW has to offer.

Lyft or Uber is ideal to get you around or over to the stadium (save on crazy parking fees). They are always around, usually with in 5 minutes.

Check in time is at 4pm. 
Check out is at 10am.

I will do my best to accommodate  early check-ins/ late check-outs depending on back to back reservations.

Listing Title: COWBOY STADIUM HOMES,LLC Corporate rentals Unit 5
Description:
This home was built in 1940.It has been remodeled but holds the charm and nostalgia with the original doors and hardwood flooring.  It is literally across the street from AT&T stadium, in the heart of the Entertainment District. Close to everything!  Check out downtown Arlington's new nightlife!  Texas Live must be seen!!!

Host will calculate additional tax for you and will message you through the Airbnb site.
Just so you are prepared, this home is prone to the noise of the stadium, so if you are a light sleeper, bring your earplugs..unless you plan to be part of it all!!

Guests have full access to the whole home with the exceptions of the garage which will remain locked.

I am usually very close as I own several homes on the street.  Outside perimeter cameras are installed that allow me to look in to ensure that all is well with the neighbors and guests are behaving according to the House Rules.

This is an older neighborhood with all homes built in the 1940s.  There are a lot of retired people and young families that live here.
PARKING:  CITY OF ARLINGTON ORDINANCE DOES NOT ALLOW ANY STREET PARKING DURING SPECIAL EVENTS.  THIS HOME HAS ENOUGH PARKING FOR 4-6 CARS STACKED IN THE DRIVEWAY.  CITY WILL TOW ANYONE PARKING ALONG THE CURB AND WILL TICKET CARS NOT PARKED ON PAVEMENT.

Walking is always an option.  Pedicabs are working when there is an event in Cowboy Stadium or Rangers Stadium.  They are fun, but you must negotiate pricing with them.  (please be fair-they work hard!)  There is an Arlington trolley that runs through the city and there is a train that goes from Dallas through Arlington to FT Worth.  There is also a visitors center next to Rangers Stadium on the corner of Randol Mill and Nolan Ryan drive. Avoid walking southwest of the home very far as there is a homeless shelter close and can lend itself to undesirables.

Prone to noise of the stadium and tailgate parties from businesses behind the home.

Listing Title: New! Home walking distance to TEXAS LIVE!
Description:
Check-In Instructions:
- Check anytime after 2:00 pm. (Let us know if any changes, we are very flexible if we have no other bookings schedule). 
- The home is accessible via keyless entry. 
- To unlock the door press the top "Schlage" button. The keypad will light up blue, type in the code, and rotate the keyhole 
- To lock the door, press the "Schlage" button and rotate the keyhole
- Please inform the Local Contact of any problems or concerns upon arrival, so we can work to address these immediately.


Check-Out Instructions:
- Check out before 11:00 am. please keep in mind we could have another booking at 2 pm the day you check out. We like to ensure we have enough time for the team to do their routine cleaning before every guest. We also want you to know if we can provide an EARLIER booking - we will! We understand life happens. we are here to help to the best of our abilities. 
- Prior to your departure, please tidy up the home by doing the following:
- Take out the trash 
- Remove all perishable items.
- Load and start the dishwasher
- Place all used linens and towels in a pile 
- Turn off all lights, electronics, and appliances
- Close and lock all windows and doors
- Additional fees will be imposed if the home is found in an unsatisfactory condition, so please return it to the condition in which you found it.

**Complete Cleaning Checklist Prior to Leaving. If the checklist is not completed fine will be given. **

I live just a few miles away from our Vacation Rental Home. I’m there to assist you in anything that you might need. You can count on me to be there! You will have complete privacy while in our home. It’s a great neighborhood. Very quiet and relaxing!

Quiet neighborhood near Globelife field, Six Flag, Texas Live, and the AT&T Stadium

There are no public transportation options here, however, rideshare services such as Uber and Lyft are available as well as a traditional taxi. There is also plenty of driveway parking. We also have a two-car garage.

Listing Title: Casa Verde B&B-5BR/3BA Sleeps 12, Pool/FirePit
Description:
This is a special house inside and out.     It sits on a gated one  acre of land in the heart of the entertainment area.  We like to think of it as a Mini-Estate.  You drive down a  long driveway to a secluded yard with roughly 30 trees.  It is a slice of the country minutes from the airport and minutes from all of the attractions. There are 5  bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, 2 large living areas, a large open kitchen.  It is the perfect house for family or friends to gather and enjoy. 3200 sq ft

The pool has a beachfront entry and many tables and chairs and a large gas grill and fire pit.  There is another patio upstairs with lounge chairs and a table and on the other side of the house another deck with a small gas grill and a smoker.

Guest have access to the entire 3200 sq ft house.  Three bedrooms upstairs.  Two have queen beds. One has 2 sets of bunk beds.  There is one full bathroom upstairs.  Downstairs there is a very large bedroom with a king bed and private bathroom, with whirlpool tub, separate shower...and heated toilet seat.  The other bedroom downstairs has a full bed and a full bathroom right outside the bedroom door.    There are also two couches that could be used as beds.

The property has a separate garage apartment above the garage that is connected to the house by a covered walkway.  We live there and usually will be available to help with any questions, concerns or to help with anything that will make your stay more enjoyable.

We are close to the airport, Hurricane Harbor, Six Flags over Texas, Ranger Stadium, AT&T Stadium, Texas Live and many restaurants and shopping areas.

There are many transportation options in our area from the Via Ride Share Service, Milo Autonomous Shuttle, Arlington Entertainment District Trolley Uber and Lyft.

Listing Title: Private Room in Main House of Ecovillage
Description:
***30 nights minimum stay***

This charming private room is in our main house within The Garden of Eden eco-village, a thriving small community dedicated to sustainability and philanthropy! With over 3 acres of land, herb & vegetable gardens, wildcrafted food and medicine,  and a handful of residents living here, the vibe is wholesome and progressive. 

You are welcome to enjoy the privacy of your room, or join us on the grounds or in the main house for activities and communal meals by donation.

This charming private room is in the center of the main house of our sustainable community. 

A queen bed (with lavender memory foam mattress topper!!), seating area, closet, and dresser are available to you in this private space.

There is a ceiling fan and extra box fans available to keep you cool in summer, as well as a window AC unit. A space heater and extra blankets are available to keep you toasty warm in winter. There is a lock on the door for your privacy and comfort. We ask a $20 deposit for the key to the lock, which we will refund when you return the key at the end of your stay.

We provide a complimentary continental breakfast for you with hot tea, seasonal fruits, a variety of organic milks & cereals, organic breads, and delicious spreads like jams and nut butters in our shared dining area of the main house.

You will have your choice of restroom facilities! We have a shared indoor bathroom right outside this room with running water, flush toilet, and a hot shower for your comfort and convenience. 

We also have some unique options available for the environment lovers to try our sustainable culture:

With 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, our home has all you need for a great and comfortable stay! 

***Bookings can only be made for stays of 30 days or longer. Absolutely no exceptions can be made***

Uber and Lyft are popular in the metroplex as well as Arlington's new ride share app Via.

This location is special because you are minutes away from some of the most popular activities for travelers to Arlington. Whether you need to be near the UTA campus or if you are going to events at the AT&T or Globe Life Stadium,  our home is optimal for your stay. Just minutes aways from major highway, it is very close to both Dallas and Fort Worth.

Listing Title: Texas Star
Description:
Incredible location only a couple of miles from the AT&T stadium, Texas Rangers, Texas Live and both Hurricane Harbor and Six Flags! Our home is like having your own resort..Pool, indoor and outdoor entertainment facilities and sleeps 8... the best of all the worlds!

The entryway of the Texas Star leads to the central open living room many amenities to relax during your stay! Enjoy watching sports or movies on the 65” TV while from the comfortable couches. Comfortable, updated, and stylishly furnished home in the heart of the Arlington Entertainment district sleeps 8-10 people and has two full baths. Walking distance to AT&T Stadium, Globe Life Park, Six Flags, Texas Live, and multiple restaurants.

The property includes free off-street parking for up to two cars. The property has a large backyard and a pleasant deck to enjoy a cup of coffee in the morning or a cocktail in the evening. A charcoal grill is also provided.

Parties are NOT allowed. This includes any party-like behavior, such as hosting more than the maximum number of people, congregating in front of the property, multiple cars parked on the street, loud music, etc. If you violate this rule, you will be asked to leave and your money will not be refunded.

We provide a starter supply of items such as toilet paper, paper towels, dishwashing soap, kitchen sponge, trash can liners, and coffee supplies, as well as laundry soap and dryer sheets for units with washer and dryer. Guests should be prepared to replenish these supplies when they run out. We also provide amenity hand and shower soaps. However, guests are encouraged to provide their own personal care toiletries, as well as kitchen supplies such as oil, spices, foil and wraps, bottled water, etc.

Listing Title: The Simple Pad
Description:
Come and rest your head in the simple living space. There is lots to do around the area just minutes away from the Cowboys Stadium, Rangers Stadium, Sixflags, Hurricane Harbor, and many little shopping strips and restaurants! 

Arlington, TX is the best place to stay if you like to be in between both main cities, Dallas and Fort Worth! Just minutes away from both cities,  you get the best of both worlds! 

The Simple Pad is also conveniently located just about 5 mins from DFW airport!

You will have full access to the entire apartment. We don’t have a tv, but we have a projector with Netflix for all your movie needs. There is access to a patio to either relax outside or to smoke. Please feel free to use the washer and dryer if you are in need. Don’t worry about cleaning, we have this covered :)

Melinda and I are available at anytime you need via text, email, or app. Please let us know how we can accommodate you!

The neighborhood is right off the freeway which makes it easy to get going fast! It’s also a great place to go for a jog in the morning! Very pleasant atmosphere with either just jogging around the block or jogging at the park down the street! Enjoy the view of the nice residential houses and bright, green landscapes!

There are many fast food restaurants within walking distance, but car ride minutes from major attractions such as, six flags, hurricane harbor, cowboys stadium, Texas Rangers stadium, and much more! Uber is your best friend! Drivers will get to you within 5 mins or less!

If you are hungry, there are quick fast food restaurants near by: McDonald’s, KFC, Taco Bell, Pollo Loco, Whataburger, Jack n the Box, Dairy Queen and many more. Qt is right up the corner for refreshments and gas. There is also a Family Dollar around the corner for quick groceries and daily essentials!

Book with confidence knowing you have your own private entrance, private garage, and an additional fence installed for your own PRIVATE BACKYARD. This Duplex is nestled in a quiet, family neighborhood  close to the major highways, restaurants ,shops and 10 min from Medical city Arlington. Has a well-equipped kitchen and sleeps up to 4 people. The Duplex is in a quiet neighborhood, but still not far from 1-20, Hwy 161, and Hwy 360.

Each unit is has it own privacy for your comfort and peace of mind.

Description:
Get the true Texas experience in this luxurious and spacious home.  Relax on any of the memory foam mattresses or watch your favorite show on 1 of the 4 Smart TV’s with Netflix or Hulu. Enjoy your morning coffee (Starbucks/Duncan Donuts) in our beautiful and fully equipped kitchen.
The AT&T Stadium is only a 3 min Walk! This home is centrally located near many restaurants, food chains, and bars that are within walking distance. Go check out Six Flags or The Parks Mall, both under 8 mins away!

Quiet hours 11 pm to 9 AM, NO sound, music, noise outside the home! Please be respectful to our neighbors!! The home is in a residential neighborhood.

Listing Title: Stylish apartment right in the heart of Arlington
Description:
Beautiful studio apartment in downtown Arlington. One block from the University of Texas at Arlington. One mile from the Cowboys and Rangers' stadiums, and Texas Live. Two and a half miles from Six Flags and Hurricane Harbor. Includes one queen size bed and one very comfortable double sofa bed. Fully equipped with washer, dryer, full kitchen, dishwasher, outdoor patio, and parking space. All brand new 2019. 450 square feet of space. 
Walk to concerts, coffee shops, and restaurants.

Coffee, tea, milk, towels, sheets, etc. will be provided. Large TV with Netflix and Amazon. Wifi service included.

Guests have their own dedicated parking space on the driveway next to the apartment. The apartment has its own self contained patio space for relaxing.

I live nearby if you need anything or have questions.

Downtown Arlington has a host of independently owned businesses within walking distance--Legal Draft brewery, Urban Alchemy Coffee and wine bar, Cartel Tacos, J. Gilligans, etc. The Levitt Pavilion is two blocks away and hosts more than 50 free concerts a year. So much to do without ever getting in your car!

Guests can walk to many restaurants, coffee shops, bars etc from the apartment. It is also one block from College Park Center, which hosts sporting events, and walking distance to the Levitt Pavilion for free outdoor concerts. Arlington does not have public transit, so if you need to venture further afield in DFW you would need to use ride service or have a car.

Listing Title: Amazing Newly Remodeled Home IN Arlington!!
Description:
$1700/ month-to-month!! 

Brand New Inside! Very nice, upscale 2 Bedroom, 2 full baths right across from Cowboys Stadium AT&T Stadium, Texas Rangers Globe Life Park and Stadium, and the New 'Live'.
The Master is HUGE and has a King bed with it's own full bathroom with double sinks, granite countertops, really large shower! The guest bedroom has 2 beds and is completely separate from the master with a bathroom right by the guest room!:) The kitchen is amazing! Must see!

Soak up the modern charm of this remodeled home! Walking distance to the AT&T stadium. Location is everything!!!

This home is a GEM! The 2nd bedroom and bathroom is on the opposite side of the home, for more privacy with your travel buddies! 2 living rooms, a very spacious BEAUTIFUL kitchen and dining room! EVERYTHING you need is HERE!

Enjoy the entire home, along with the HUGE backyard.

Always available via text or phone call!

Very quiet neighborhood. No traffic from the the stadium, because parking in the neighborhood is not permitted if you do not live in or rent!

Cars are only permitted to park in the driveway. You can Uber literally anywhere in the DFW area from this location if preferred. Walk just 2 blocks to get to the AT&T stadium!

*Please note: The City of Arlington is very strict regarding short-term rentals/vacation homes. The city charges a 9% hotel occupancy tax on top of the state tax Airbnb collects. I have to send all my guests an additional 9% payment request for each booking.

Absolutely no parties are allowed.

We want our guests to relax and enjoy a peaceful stay! I would love to recommend any restaurants or activities for you and your family. Just ask!

Description:
Updated & spacious  home in the HEART of ARLINGTON/Stadium!

4 Bedrooms / 2 Bathrooms / Gated Backyard

Prime location, plenty of parking & all the comforts of home! Fully stocked kitchen, games, WIFI/cable, full size washer/dryer & lots of outdoor living!

2 MILES FROM AT&T STADIUM & GLOBE LIFE PARK

AT&T Stadium - Convention Center - Will Rogers, Downtown - TCU - NAS - Six Flags - TX Motor Speedway - Globe Life Park - Stockyards - Hurricane Harbor

Welcome to Arlington, TX - Home of the Dallas Cowboys & Texas Rangers, SIx Flags & Water Parks!

This thoughtfully designed, unique retreat is perfect for out of town visitors & staycationers alike! The Mill House is bright & fun in a classic style with a twist of Texas!

The kitchen is stocked with all the comforts of home - from updated appliances to dinnerware, flatware, and glassware to an array of gadgets & gizmos you'll need to gather around the table. You'll also find your wake-up cure in the kitchen with a Keurig coffee maker stocked with all the fixings!

The living & dining areas are bright, open & functional. And, most importantly, if you need to stay connected during your stay, you'll find high speed WIFI.

For your convenience, there is a laundry area with a washer & dryer and laundry/cleaning supplies.

The backyard is the perfect place to enjoy early morning quiet time, midday picnic lunches & evening BBQs! There is a propane grill for outdoor cooking, outdoor tables with plenty of seating and a fire pit for marshmallow roasting.

When you're ready to turn in, you'll find 4 bedrooms with the following accommodations:
Bedroom 1: 1 King Bed
Bedroom 2: 2 Queen Beds
Bedroom 3: 2 Queen Beds
Bedroom 4: 3 Sets of Twin Bunk Beds
The bunk room is designed with fun & fort building in mind! There is room for game playing, movie watching and lots of R&R!

Please contact us with questions - We'd love to welcome you with a big HOWDY!

-Near AT&T Stadium and Globe Life Park

-Plenty of eating establishments nearby

Listing Title: **AT&T Stadium** “Large Family Suite”
Description:
2.9 miles from AT&T Stadium and minutes from the Rangers Ballpark, six-flags/Hurricane Harbor and 15min from DFW Airport. This apartment is large, newly remodeled and beautifully decorated but it is the complex that stands out! This gated community features a gym, club house with pool table, Tennis/basketball court, 2 pools, hot tub and a green belt of vegetation and duck ponds around the complex that isolate you from the city outside.  Get more out of your stay with the Large Family Suite!

This apartment features brand new appliances, a spacious floor plan and plenty of sleeping accommodations to keep your group comfortable! This apartment is full of family friendly features such as in-unit washer/dryer, 3 separate closets to store belongings and most importantly separate bedroom and family room entrances to the bathroom so no one has to walk through the bedroom to use the bathroom! This gated complex is not only relaxing but safe and offers ample parking for multiple vehicles.

Guests can access all parts of the apartment itself and has access to apartment amenities.

I try to always be available to my guests by phone or through the app and even in person if needed.

Other than being conveniently located in Arlington, what makes this apartment standout is the surrounding property and its features. The complex resembles more of a retirement community than a typical Arlington apartment complex. The community of people here are refined, friendly and safe! This apartment was laid out with a family in mind. Truly the perfect place to host a family!

There is a wealth of public transportation available but I recommend using Uber if you do not have transportation of your own.

Bar Louie and Boomerjacks are popular in the Highlands. There is a small region near the college campus that offers unique bars, arcades, and food. A local favorite is the Free Play arcade which offers drinks and classic arcade games and the Urban Alchemy Coffee + Wine Bar. J. Gilligan's and the Grease Monkey are also popular spots for a burger and beer. The Parks Mall is close to the Highlands and offers a great place for shopping. The mall also offers ice skating and another movie theater. Round 1 is connected to the mall and is a fun place for bowling, pool, and a new-age style arcade. Alley Cats is near the mall. Listing Title: Comfy Arlington Hideout. Near Everything You Want!
Description:
Cleanliness is in our DNA.
COVID-19 pandemic has required us to raise our standards to an even higher level. 

Cozy in comfort and with style. This complex is a quiet/safe neighborhood. Full size kitchen, full washer/dryer to help you feel right at home. 

Free parking. Outdoor space for walking & jogging on trails, bbq pits, and playgrounds in the complex. Racetrak store, Taco Casa, and Whataburger, CVS Pharmacy. 

Minutes away from DFW Airport, Six Flags, Globe Life Park, and MANY restaurants.

Queen size bed to get some rest after your long days. 

Big comfy sofa with lots of room and love. 

Huge smart tv to help you unwind from the outside world. 

Aromatherapy oils in the air make the environment feel serene and peaceful. With humble earth tones to help you rest from your busy day. 

Clean washer and dryer to help you stay fresh in your travels.

I am available whenever you have questions! Please just call.

Easy access to I-20 and also highway 360. Five minutes away from I-30 if you wanna visit Downtown Dallas it’s only 20 minutes away. 

5-10 minutes from AT&T Stadium,  Texas Live, Ranger Stadium, Arlington Highlands, Tesla supercharger, Esports Stadium, and Parks Mall. 

Texas live is a vibrant entertainment center with cocktails bars, variety restaurants, dance floors, and gigantic sports TVs. 

 Arlington Highlands is a shopping center with many stores, bars, restaurants, and entertainment places like movie theaters and bowling. 

Esports Stadium 100,000 square foot venue LARGEST ESPORTS FACILITY IN THE UNITED STATES.

Your own car if possible. However Uber and Lyft are fast and easy. 

Arlington also has ride share vans. If you need call to get pricing.

Swimming Pools
Doggie Bark Park
Gated Community
Tot Lot & Playground
Sand Volleyball Court
2 1/2 Mile Jogging Trail
Picnic Area with BBQ Grills

Quiet Bedroom for a very relaxing and comfortable night. You’ll have your own private bedroom, a shared bathroom, a shared living room. Listing Title: Charming Modern Condo- Entertainment District #821
Description:
Mid-Century Modern Condo-VERY CLEAN!! Near AT&T Stadium, Global Life Park, Six Flags, Hurricane Harbor, University of Texas at Arlington

Our priority is that your stay is both pleasant and relaxing. We have carefully picked quality items in our condo to ensure an excellent experience such as a comfortable memory-foam mattress, a cozy sofa, hypoallergenic sheets/pillows, organic bath towels, and organic soaps.

Guest have access to our entire condo and community grounds.

We are available whenever you need us through the messaging inbox or through email.

Our condo is roughly 5 minutes from AT&T Stadium and Global Life Park. It’s also very close to Great America and Hurricane Harbor, along with numerous great restaurants and night life activities.

Most attractions and venues located in Arlington are accessible through walking or Uber/Lyft drivers.

The community grounds are very quiet, peaceful and relaxing.

Listing Title: Relaxing Bed mid DFW near AT&T Stadium & Six Flags
Description:
Comfy Bedroom for a very relaxing night. You’ll have your own private bedroom, a shared bathroom, a shared living room. This home is located 25 minutes from Dallas downtown and 25 mins from Fort Worth downtown giving you the option to visit either as you please. This stay includes comfortable couches, a workspace area, and a TV. We have an available microwave, fridge, and a full kitchen at your convenience. I also stay in this home in another room.

This room gives you access to a living room, and a lounge area outside of your room where you can work, interact with others, or watch TV and enjoy a very chill night or day

I love hearing stories from all travelers and guests so if you like engaging with strangers and learning more from others then I’ll be available to talk as well.

I can also recommend good places to visit on your stay. When I came to live here 2 years ago, I didn’t know anyone so I spent a lot of time learning amazing places downtown and elsewhere to go so I’ll gladly share.

Please let me know if you have any specific requests/accommodations and I'll see what I can provide!

The neighborhood is very calm and relaxed. You will rarely hear any noise. The neighborhood is beautiful and has sidewalks where you can walk around or sit and enjoy the beautiful nature. We are close to major highways for you to go wherever you need to either in your car or using rideshare apps.

On your way, you get to enjoy the Six Flags and AT&T stadium scenery and multiple other attractions

It is a pretty easy place to get to if you are trying to use ridesharing apps and you will get one in 5min average and it is cheap to go downtown and all the other amazing places you might want to visit.

The neighborhood is very calm and relaxed. You will rarely hear any noise. The neighborhood is beautiful and has sidewalks where you can walk around or sit and enjoy the beautiful nature. We are close to major highways for you to go wherever you need to either in your car or using rideshare apps.

On your way, you get to enjoy the Six Flags and AT&T stadium scenery and multiple other attractions

Free Wi-Fi, Spectrum cable TV,  and a Xbox 360!
While here you are 0.6 miles from Cowboys Stadium, eSports Arena, Globe Life Field. Only 2 miles to Six Flags and Hurricane Harbor. Conveniently located 15 min from DFW Airport.

The house was designed by my grandmother, and has been in our family since day one. It retains 90% of its original decor, including all carpet, wall papers, bed spreads, furniture, drapes, etc.

Listing Title: Cowboys Casa!! ~Walk to stadium!~
Description:
Enjoy our lovely home where you have the entire house to yourself! 3 bedrooms/2 bathrooms. The Master has a Queen bed with it's own bath with TV in this bedroom. 2nd bedroom has a queen bed (no tv in this room) and 3rd bedroom has two double beds (no TV in this bedroom), with a full tub, shower bathroom across the hallway. The cozy home has two spacious living rooms with TV's in both Living Rooms. There is a wood burning fireplace, full size washer/dryer and a wonderful  kitchen!

The quaint kitchen and dining room has all of your cooking needs with microwave, oven, pots, pans, plates, glasses, etc.. or you can choose to sit outside on the covered patio and cook on the charcoal grill with plenty of grass for the kids to play.

Guests can reach me by call or text anytime!

*Please note: The City of Arlington is very strict regarding short-term rentals/vacation homes. The city charges a 9% hotel occupancy tax on top of the state tax Airbnb collects. I have to send all my guests an additional 9% payment request for each booking.

LOCATION, LOCATION. You can see AT&T Stadium from the front yard and you will NOT need a car to go to the game, just walk to it across the street. There is a view of Six Flags and The ballpark at Arlington as well from the front yard. Free Wifi & Direct TV. We have other rentals nearby as well as Ft. Worth approx. 25 min. away near the stockyards, Downtown Ft. Worth, TCU, & Will Rogers Coliseum.

Listing Title: Private Penthouse in Sustainable Community
Description:
***30 nights minimum stay***

Our luxurious penthouse can sleep 1-16 people! It is the upstairs master suite in our main house within The Garden of Eden, a thriving community dedicated to sustainability and philanthropy!

With over 3 acres of land, herb & vegetable gardens, wildcrafted food and medicine, and a handful of residents living here, the vibe is wholesome and progressive. 

Enjoy the privacy of your room, or join us on the grounds or in the main house for communal meals by donation.

This beautiful penthouse has a number of unique and luxurious amenities! The amazing artisan floor is hand laid with decoupage paper, and painted with delicate touches. The room is decorated in a rich jewel tone kasbah style. There is a private bathroom right outside the French doors. The penthouse suite opens into the private master bathroom. We can bring in more mattresses to accommodate parties of any size. We even have one of 2 king sized beds set up in a copper pyramid!

This master suite opens to its private master bathroom with a relaxing jacuzzi hot tub, separate toilet closet, double sinks, and double shower with super hot water. These are wonderful modern amenities that only you will have access too, and  you are also welcome to sample our refreshing outdoor well shower if you wish to try our sustainable lifestyle! 

We currently have the bedroom space set up with two king sized beds - one of which is within a copper pyramid! The pyramid is a beautiful structure that is amazing for meditation, because the shape and material is a great conductor of subtle energies.

Description:

Listing Title: 4 bds for Sheltering-In-Place/Social Distancing
Description:
Whether it's you and 3 other fellow students that need a place to stay outside the dorms, or you need to keep yourself away from the older family members, we've got you covered.  This house is homey and guaranteed to be a better option for a long-term stay than a hotel. Weekly and monthly discounts available.

The entire house was renovated last year, but the original hardwood floors and splash walls have been tastefully kept, giving it a rustic feel with a modern touch. You will have access to all four bedrooms, three of which have their own private entrances. Two king beds, two queen beds, and a queen sofa bed in the living room combine to accommodate up to 10 guests. Towels, shampoo, and body wash are provided in the bathrooms.

The kitchen is equipped with pots and pans, knives, spatulas, dishes, and silverware for you to prepare and enjoy a meal with family and friends. Free coffee, both regular and decaf, are provided to give your morning a boost.

Free wifi is provided, along with Netflix, Disney+, Hulu, and an antenna to capture local channels. Want to have some fun off the grid? Board games are available to entertain friends and family for hours. Should you need to do laundry, you will also have access to the washer and dryer.

Guests will have access to all the rooms in the house.

The driveway of the house can accommodate up to 3 vehicles.

You will have the entire place to yourself, but I will be available by phone or text for any questions.

The open layout offers a sleek kitchen, large living room, and a sunny breakfast nook - a completely private space!

Brand new everything with a fully remodeled stainless steel kitchen and bathroom. You'll enjoy the lavish white and grey finishes that give a sense of trend and luxury. This is a home that is on one side of a duplex. It is a completely separated and private space from neighbors.

Open living room has a Smart TV with complimentary Netflix and streaming channels!

Convenience is a highlight for this home! You'll be able to enjoy all that the city has to offer and return to serenity and privacy at the end of the day. Family-oriented neighborhood with an Ice Cream Truck that drives by around 2:30 PM everyday!

You'll have access to the entire home/unit. No shared spaces in this beautiful gem. Off-Street Parking only with two car maximum.

Arlington is a driving city. Recommend car rental, Uber or Lyft (very popular and cheap!).

Absolutely NO parties, events or gatherings allowed. Maximum 4 person occupancy. Quiet family neighborhood. Any parties suspected, found (or in the event of a neighbor complaint) will be subjected to entire security deposit ($500) taken. 

Strict NO smoking in home.

Listing Title: HM Homes Hostel #3 (Long Term Available)
Description:
This is a beautiful home in the Arlington area  It is a quiet place with a park right across the street. There are fast food restaurants and a Tom Thumb within walking distance. It is approximately 11 minutes away driving distance from the AT&T Cowboy Stadium. Everything you need is pretty much around the corner.

This place is really cozy the most wonderful beds you will ever sleep on. All of my bed are either memory foam or Tempur-pedic. Everything you need is right around the corner from restaurants to a food market. We keep this place as clean and spotless as we can and have someone come in everyday to make sure of it. Due to Coronavirus we are taking safety precautions.

Guest have access to the whole house and the room they were assigned to. Please respect other guest privacy. The only part of the house guest do not have access to is the garage.

I don’t mind talking to the guest if it’s a emergency or something that you need for the house. Please call at anytime my number will be on the chalkboard in the kitchen.

When you arrive you will notice that there is a park across the street. The neighborhoods is very family orientated. You will see people jogging during the day or riding bikes. Tom Thumb is only a few blocks away there are many restaurants and financial institutions less then 5 minutes away.

You can take a bike around. Things are really close by for restaurants. For the Cowboy stadium you will need to hop in the car that is approximately 11 min away.

Please keep the noice to a minimum because you will be sharing with other guest. I ask that you respect them and their privacy. PLEASE HAVE A GREAT STAY!!!

It is approximately 11 minutes away driving distance from the AT&T Cowboy Stadium. Everything you need is pretty much around the corner.

This place is really cozy the most wonderful beds you will ever sleep on. All of my bed are either memory foam or Tempur-pedic. Everything you need is right around the corner from restaurants to a food market. We keep this place as clean and spotless as we can and have someone come in everyday to make sure of it. Due to Coronavirus we are taking safety precautions.

Guest have access to the whole house and the room they were assigned to. Please respect other guest privacy. The only part of the house guest do not have access to is the garage.

I don’t mind talking to the guest if it’s a emergency or something that you need for the house. Please call at anytime my number will be on the chalkboard in the kitchen.

When you arrive you will notice that there is a park across the street. The neighborhoods is very family orientated. You will see people jogging during the day or riding bikes. Tom Thumb is only a few blocks away there are many restaurants and financial institutions less then 5 minutes away.

You can take a bike around. Things are really close by for restaurants. For the Cowboy stadium you will need to hop in the car that is approximately 11 min away.

Please keep the noice to a minimum because you will be sharing with other guest. I ask that you respect them and their privacy. PLEASE HAVE A GREAT STAY!!!

Listing Title: “The LaValse” A Luxury Suite
Description:
My place is your home away from home, we all have different styles but we all have the same goal which is to be as comfortable anywhere we choose to stay as we are in our own homes . Thanks for considering “The LaValse Luxury Suite” for your stay!

During the winter season which is now the pool area is still closed,  however you are free to walk about the property and jog the  trails if weather permits.

I try to make myself available at all times before and after any check in, however we all might have emergency situations which might arise at any time. If I am not available you can contact my cohost. If you send a message within the app and do not get a response within 15 minutes please call my cell directly. We are here for you and we consider each and everyone of our guest family.

We are close to multiple shopping centers that contains a variety of stores, Including the “Grand Prairie Outlets”. We are also minutes away from a variety of different eateries and restaurants along the Highway!

All guest are allowed to park in visitor parking, however each vehicle must be registered every 24 Hours, and a screenshot of the green confirmation circles is highly recommended.
Instructions for Parking will be including in Welcome Instructions after Booking! 

If you do not have transportation Lyft and Uber are options if you do need transportation prior to your stay please let us know and we will make any and all efforts to help find services that you may be able to use.

We should also be adding a few more items to make your experience as effortless as possible.

We do have a bar located within the unit, however any item that is opened will be charged to your card. Inventory on bar items are done before check in and after check in.

Listing Title: Cozy 2 BR North Arlington Condo Near ATT Stadium
Description:
This cozy condo is a 2 bed 1.5 bath on the 2nd story only minutes away from all of Arlington’s best attractions including Hurricane Harbor, Six Flags Over Texas, AT&T Stadium, Globelife Park and Texas Live! This space is perfect for a family vacation or a couple’s getaway!

You will have access to the entire place so you can make yourself at home! 
KITCHEN: Fully equipped kitchen with stove, oven, dishwasher and fridge. Coffee & tea provided. Full size washer & dryer directly off the kitchen. 
DINING ROOM: Round table with 4 chairs. If you need more table space, we can install a leaf to the table and add an extra 2 seats before your stay. 
PATIO: Beautiful patio with a bistro table to sit at and enjoy your morning coffee. 
LIVING ROOM: Sofa and two arm chairs,  50” Roku TV with access to Netflix, Hulu, Sling TV etc. Wifi. 
BEDROOM #1: Double bed with two nightstands, closet and dresser, the hallway half bath is right outside of this room.  
BEDROOM #2: Queen bed with 2 nightstands and closet, Master bathroom with shower is attached. BATHROOMS: Bathrooms are equipped with towels, toilet paper, blow dryer and hand soap.  First Aid kit provided in master bathroom.

Must climb stairs - 1 flight of stairs with a landing in-between. Surveillance or recording devices on property - There is a Google Nest Doorbell installed at the front door and it will be on.

For maintenance and support, please call 855-251-2268 or email us at hello@avenuewestdallas.com.

Our condo is within walking distance to local grocery stores and restaurants.

5 Minutes away from the Cowboys Stadium, Texas Live, Rangers Park, Water Park, and 6 Flags etc.  All the food, bars, shopping is also nearby.

please contact host via inbox the day before arrival to discuss checkin and out times due to prior guest stay and cleaning crew time period.  Communication is key for a healthy stay. Listing Title: BIG Master Bdrm w/ Prvt Bath.  More Rooms Availbl
Description:
This master bedroom and private bathroom is nestled facing the backyard of the house.  The house sits on .25 acre of land, and has 5 Texas pecan trees.  The backyard is totally private, due to the tall plush plants that encompass it.  The neighborhood is in the heart of the city, and all major shopping, entertainment, and business.  At the same time, it's on a hidden street, making it a quiet street, with low traffic.  The neighbors are mostly retired people who are very friendly.

I'm a phone call away, 24x7.

The house is close to Whole Foods, the mall, bars, restaurants, and the AT&T Cowboys Stadium, and Six Flags, and Rangers Stadium.
The neighborhood is full of mature frees, well-kept lawns, and friendly people walking their dogs.

Centrally located, the house is a short distance to 2 interstate highways.

In addition to this Private Master Bedroom and Bathroom, 3 other bedrooms are available for rent.  Message me if you would like to reserve those as well.

Reach out to me if you're interested in having an additional room and a private entry!

Listing Title: Private 2 bed/2Bath Condo in Hotspot of Arlington
Description:
Modern style 2 bedroom 2 bathroom first floor apartment with private entrance and private outdoor patio. Master bedroom with closets, bathroom w/garden tup, Washer & Dryer. Fridge, Coffee, and everything for basic cooking for long stays. Comfortable living room w/large sofa can be turned to sleeper sofa. The unit has High-Speed Internet with WiFi, Smart TVs in both rooms for watching Netflix, Hulu, and all streaming services available for your entertainment with HD antenna for local channels.

This space is a home away from home! Completely private first floor apartment with full kitchen, living & dining, and master suite with huge bathroom, closets, and garden tub. Smart door lock for entry allows ease of access as well as open check-in requirements as we will not require you to meet with anyone. Back private patio can be used at your discretion and is not shared by others.

You will have full and private access to the entire apartment.  Additionally, all of the amenities are shared by the complex, and you will be provided a key card to use these amenities at your will within the complexes time and use restrictions.

We will be available to assist with anything you need, and otherwise leave you fully with your uninterrupted privacy.  Access to the unit, check-in & out, and communication will be fully automated with smart locks and a unique access code for a seamless experience! We are a property management group local in Mansfield with over 13 years of property management experience.  We will not be in the neighborhood, but will be readily available and in the area should anything arise.  We will supply you with all the contact information you need to get ahold of us, and we have multiple people on staff so you can be served as quickly as possible.

Many luxurious amenities present in the complex will be available to you during your stay. Some of these amenities include:
- 2 Assigned Parking Spaces
- 3 separate swimming pools with Jacuzzi Hot Tubs
- Lighted Tennis

Listing Title: Cozy Waterfront Extended-Stay Sanctuary near UTA
Description:
We offer you a bright, cozy bedroom in our comfortable waterfront ranch home. Set in a quiet, safe, upscale neighborhood in the heart of Arlington, we're convenient to all amenities DFW has for you to enjoy. A local law limits us to hosting guests for a minimum of 30 days, so we're a perfect home-away-from-home for your business or family extended stay.

Your private room has wall-to-wall carpeting, an ample closet, a large window overlooking the spacious front lawn and garden bed, and a ceiling fan.  It is furnished with a firm single bed, a desk and office chair, a 4-drawer dresser, 2 bed-side tables, 3 lamps, and a comfortable rocking chair.... This room is only available to female guests because it shares the connected full bath (shower & tub) with your host, whose room is on the other side of the bathroom with its own access door. However, male guests may occupy this room and share the master bath across the hall if the occupant of the master suite is also male.

Your accommodations include access to all common rooms of the house -- a fully-equipped electric kitchen, free laundry room, comfortably appointed family living room with flat-screen Roku TV,  a well-shaded back yard with waterfront patio, and a front porch perfect for watching the world go by.

My hosting style is casual, like my furniture, and you are free to interact with me as much or as little as you choose. I do enjoy socializing with my guests, but I will always respect your privacy when you are home. I am never farther away than a phone call if you need assistance and happy to make suggestions about local recreation and entertainment opportunities, shopping, restaurants, and other useful resources.

The Lakewood Addition of Arlington is a lovely, quiet, safe, shady neighborhood of upscale waterfront residences. Description:
Welcome to my quaint house near ATT and Cowboys stadium. Enjoy your quiet and private guest room. Very quiet neighborhood and friendly roommate who is currently here for a long term stay. Fully stocked kitchen for long term stay guests only. Please no food or drink in the livingroom. Please use the newly renovated bathroom across the hallway with the #2 so that we can maintain Covid compliance. Mattress is covered with a plastic cover and is sanitized before and after each guest. Long term stays ONLY: kitchen, laundry

Short term stays ONLY: bedroom, bathroom, livingroom

Need help or have questions about your stay? Message me on the Airbnb app!

Quiet hours begin after 10PM where the alarm will be set to ensure guest safety and a comfortable nights sleep.

Listing Title: Arlington (Min From UTA, AT&T Stadium, Six Flags)
Description:
Soon to be a historic landmark for being one of the first houses ever built in Arlington! 

Located in the College Park District, this large and cozy home is perfect for those coming to town for a family day at Six Flags & Hurricane Harbor, a college visit to UTA, or to catch the Cowboys at the AT&T stadium. When you come back to unwind, you can enjoy a bottle of complimentary wine and watch your favorite show on Hulu, Netflix, or Disney+!

Please note that this property is shared with a man named Dicky who lives in a trailer behind the fence in the backyard. He's super friendly and works a lot on the yard and in his garden. 

This house has four bedrooms, two with king size beds and two with queen size beds. 3 of the bedrooms have their own Roku TV. There are two full bathrooms with shampoo, conditioner, and body wash dispensers and a hair dryer available for use. The living room has a smart TV with access to Hulu, Netflix and Disney+. The kitchen is equipped with pots, pans, cooking utensils and dishware if you feel like cooking! We also have a keurig for our coffee lovers. There is an air mattress available upon request to accommodate up to 10 guests. 

The house is renovated but is still an older house so it has its quirks. For example, some of the doors get stuck and require a little more of a push and there is an unfinished walking path made of bricks near the driveway. Please do not try to use this path.

Guest have access to all rooms in the house and the outdoor areas.

I like to provide guests with as much privacy as possible, so it is likely that we will not meet guests in person. This allows guests to enjoy the space and get their moneys worth! I am available upon request for any issues or questions!

This house is located close to all the major attractions that Arlington has to offer along with plenty of restaurants and bars. 

University of Texas at Arlington- 1 min drive (walking distance) 
AT&T Stadium- 5 min drive 
Globe Life Park- 5 min drive 
Live

Listing Title: Stylish Apt near AT&T Stadium/Six Flags/Tx Live
Description:
Great clean, stylish place within the Entertainment District of Arlington, Texas! Walking distance to AT&T Stadium, the Global Life Stadium, and a short drive to Six Flags. 

Additionally, there are great eats near by which include Torchy’s Tacos, The Social House, Tiff’s Treats, and SO much more! 

About 20 minutes to Downtown Fort Worth and the Stockyards. 

Also about a 15 minute drive to DFW International Airport.

You will have access to the fitness center from 10:00am-6:00pm. 

There is a full bathroom and full kitchen. 

You can sit back and relax in the living room and outside balcony.

Entryway requires climbing 1 flight of stairs.

Guests have access to entire space!

We LOVE to hear from our guests. You could call us, email us, or send us a message on the AirBnb site!

The apartment is about a mile from the AT&T Stadium and Global Life Park (within walking distance). 

Six Flags is 2 miles away as well!

Downtown Fort Worth, the Fort Worth Convention Center  and the Stockyards are 20 minutes away.

Only a 15 minute drive to DFW International Airport.

Our guests will park for free in any space that is not marked ‘reserved’.

We take special care in cleaning and sanitizing. All linens, comforters, and throw blankets are thoroughly washed after every guest. There is never a time where any of these items are reused for another guest. Additionally, pillows are washed regularly. We hope our extra efforts in cleaning will give our guests peace of mind and add to a great experience and enjoyable stay at our place!

PLEASE NOTE: if you have any additional guests on your reservation, be sure to add/invite each guest to your trip and ask them to submit a valid ID if their ID has not already been verified on their profile. All guests must be verified BEFORE check in instructions are sent.

Listing Title: Furnished room, private bath and cleaning service
Description:
Spacious furnished room with private bathroom and closet in a large house in quiet neighborhood in Arlington, TX. Near UTA, downtown Fort Worth, and Rangers and Cowboys stadiums.

Beautiful and inviting home. This home has been updated with new flooring, paint, and remodeled bathrooms.  Excellent central location with access to everything the DFW area has to offer. 10 min car ride to Parks Mall, Dallas Cowboys AT&T stadium, and new Globe Life Park stadium. Only 20 minutes away from Downtown Fort Worth and historic stock yards via toll free I-30. 30 minutes away from downtown Dallas via toll free I-30.

This is the perfect alternative to a hotel/motel bedroom. Why spend $$$ for a hotel room when you're barely in it? Save some money and stay at my place.

The neighborhood is a nice and quiet residential neighborhood where you can see people going for a jog or stroll in the evening. There is an Aldi, Tom Thumb, Kroger and Starbucks within a 1.5 mile radius (4 min drive).

Car is the recommended mode of transportation. There is free parking as the home has a large driveway. 

Uber and Lyft are also available in the area and can be another transportation method.

Listing Title: ⍟Fun Cozy House By AT&T⍟Comfy Beds⍟Awesome Hosts
Description:
Spacious house 1/2 mile from AT&T stadium within entertainment district (Six Flags, Texas Live, Rangers). Entire house is for guests and offers an affordable, clean, and relaxing place to stay. This historic house was built in 1919 but was recently well remodeled. It is a great sized house for an Airbnb stay and is centrally located not only in Arlington, but also in the middle of the DFW metroplex.

The two Bedrooms: 
- Queen size bed, night stand, overhead ceiling fan
Please note: the space is exactly as pictured, and we do not have dressers or chairs in the bedrooms. 
One bedroom has a foosball table

Kitchen: 
- Full size, functional space. 
- Full size fridge/freezer, dishwasher, oven, stove, and microwave. 
- Basic pots/pans as well as utensils, coffee mugs, and glasses provided. 
- Keurig coffee maker (no coffee pot) that takes k-pods. 

Dining Area: 
- Next to the kitchen, with a table and chairs 

Living Room:
- One sofa that also functions as a pull out bed (sleeps 2)
- Coffee table
- One oversize chair
- TV (please note, we do not have cable, but rather a smart TV to connect to 
    your subscriptions)

Outside: 
- The home was built in 1919! It has been recently remodeled but is an older, historic home. Please see pictures.

Entire home is yours!

Access and Check-in/Check-out Times: 
-  Keypad Entry
-  Check in anytime after 4pm
-  Check out anytime before 11am
-  Unfortunately we are no longer able to accomodate early check-in/late 
    check-out out of respect to our cleaners schedule. 

Neighborhood/Surrounding Area: 
-  Our home is located in an older working class neighborhood a few blocks 
    from the AT&T stadium. Please ensure this fits your needs prior to booking.

Listing Title: Professionally maintained apt | 1BR in Arlington
Description:
Stay for 30+ nights (minimum nights and rates are FIRM) where you’ll have the entire apartment all to yourself at Providence In The Park. The apartment has beautiful finishes and comes fully outfitted with kitchen, bedroom, & bathroom essentials. Please note, the furnishings & room details WILL VARY as the unit is set up for you upon booking. We are an experienced professional hospitality company that works directly with the property to transform vacant units into your home away from home.

We take the health and safety of guests seriously. Between each stay, the apartment is thoroughly cleaned and sanitized following guidance from the CDC. Cleaners wear protective garments (e.g., mask, gloves) and wipe surfaces, cabinet handles, door knobs, etc. with cleaning solutions that follow CDC guidance. All linens, dishware, glassware and silverware are also washed between stays. Cleaning products and tools are provided so you can clean and sanitize as well.

We require Hosts and Guests to wear masks during any in-person interaction.

You’ll be staying in your own 718 square-foot,  fully-furnished apartment including WiFi, smart TV, and all utilities (cable TV available by inquiry for additional cost). The floor plan provides an open living space with a fully-equipped kitchen, living room, and bathroom. The apartment is set up just for guests so it can truly feel like your home during your stay and there’s plenty of space to set up your laptop or stretch out on the couch.

You’ll have the apartment completely to yourself and can access building amenities (public health guidance permitting) that are included in your reservation (e.g., if parking is not purchased, parking access will not be granted).

Who knows, you may love it so much you decide to stay longer or move-in permanently!

We are a professional hospitality provider working in partnership with the property so you can feel completely welcome. Should you need anything fixed in your apartment, however, do contact us

Listing Title: Beautiful Condo in the Entertainment District
Description:
This beautiful condo has been completely renovated/updated w/ all new paint, flooring, counter-tops & appliances. Prime location,  just minutes from AT&T Stadium, Globe Life Park, Texas Live, Six-Flags, many restaurants, shopping, I-30, & SH-360.  Its a quiet, mostly retired community that’s been well maintained.ask No pets/no smoking.  Access to pool. Reserved/covered parking. Washer/dryer included. Unlimited WiFi access.
MIN. 30 DAY RENTAL

It offers a gated front porch area to greet you and any visitor where you can relax with your favorite beverage. The newly remodeled, open floor-plan concept and high ceilings give the living area a welcoming and conversational setting. Other amazing amenities include: new appliances and granite counter tops in the kitchen, enclosed wet bar, new furniture and modern decor throughout, new king and queen Sealy Posturepedic mattresses, full-sized washer and dryer, and covered parking for two vehicles.

Condo has a private entrance with two covered parking spaces.  There are two patios to enjoy a cup of coffee in the mornings or the cool breeze of the Texas evenings.

We are available on site when needed.  We are able to answer any questions any guest may have.

It is within a short walking distance to AT&T Stadium, Globe Life Park, Texas Life, Six Flags, Hurricane Harbor, various parks, shopping, a variety of restaurants, and only a 15-minute drive to either downtown Dallas or Fort Worth.

There is not access to public transportation close to the area but Uber and Lyft are always 5 minutes out.

You’ll have the apartment completely to yourself and can access building amenities (public health guidance permitting) that are included in your reservation (e.g., if parking is not purchased, parking access will not be granted).

Who knows, you may love it so much you decide to stay longer or move-in permanently!

Listing Title: Fully updated retreat w/ a furnished patio near AT&T Stadium & Globe Life Field
Description:
Stadium Station Welcome to Stadium Station, a completely updated and fully-furnished 1,400 square foot home near all the top attractions in Arlington. The well-equipped, full kitchen, complete with a breakfast bar, is perfect for channeling your inner chef and preparing cost-saving, homemade meals for you and your group. You can even upgrade your mealtimes using the private gas grill on your furnished patio. And then dine together indoors at the table with seating for six. Relax in your living room and watch your favorite shows on the smart, flatscreen TV before heading out to explore your surroundings. What's nearby: Stadium Station definitely lives up to its name as it is just a few blocks from the Cowboys Stadium (AT&T Stadium) and Globe Life Field (home of the National Finals Rodeo in December). You'll be right between Dallas and Fort Worth, plus there's no shortage of restaurants and friendly bars nearby in case you don't feel like switching on your stove. And when available, enjoy a fun-filled afternoon at Six Flags Over Texas, one of the most popular amusement parks in America, located just a couple miles west. Things to know: Central air conditioning *A surveillance camera is installed at this home No dog(s) are welcome in this home. No other animals are allowed without specific Vacasa approval.
Parking notes: There is free parking for 4 vehicles. Four spots in the driveway.
Security camera details:
Damage waiver: The total cost of your reservation for this Property includes a damage waiver fee which covers you for up to $2,000 of accidental damage to the Property or its contents (such as furniture, fixtures, and appliances) as long as you report the incident to the host prior to checking out. More information can be found from the "Additional rules" on the checkout page. Other permit number: 20 - 088713

Listing Title: **BEST LOCATION** Walk to AT&T Stdm/Globe Life**
Description:
Our home is ideally located in the Entertainment district. You can save on parking fees and very conveniently walk to AT&T stadium. The home is only minutes  from major attractions like Globe Life  (Rangers) field, Texas Live, Six flags, about 15mins to DFW airport. It is surrounded by lots of restaurants & shopping options and its only minutes from I-30.
Enjoy WIFI smart TV, lovely rooms & kitchen and a big backyard for outdoor entertaining. Dishes, silverware etc are available and big parking.

Guests will have access to the entire home. Children are able to use the swing set in the backyard. 

DISCLOSURE: there is a pool in the backyard that has a gate around it on the property that is currently inoperable and guests will not be able to use it at this time.

Guests have access to the entire home. There is a pool in the backyard that is not accessible at this time.

We are available through any communication line but prefer to speak through the message thread in the app. We to do our very best to respond to messages quickly so our guests do not have to wait to hear from us. We take hosting seriously and understand that it’s our job to ensure our guests have an enjoyable and comfortable stay.

Our place is located in the Entertainment District of Arlington, Texas. It is a mile or less from Six Flags, Global Life Park, AT&T Stadium, Texas LIVE, and many restaurants. This location is unbeatable!

Parking is free on premise. Uber and Lyft is also easily accessible as this is a busy area for entertainment and events.

Listing Title: Professionally maintained apt | 1BR in Arlington
Description:

We require Hosts and Guests to wear masks during any in-person interaction.

You’ll be staying in your own 718 square-foot,  fully-furnished apartment including WiFi, smart TV, and all utilities (cable TV available by inquiry for additional cost). The floor plan provides an open living space with a fully-equipped kitchen, living room, and bathroom. The apartment is set up just for guests so it can truly feel like your home during your stay and there’s plenty of space to set up your laptop or stretch out on the couch.

You’ll have the apartment completely to yourself and can access building amenities (public health guidance permitting) that are included in your reservation (e.g., if parking is not purchased, parking access will not be granted).

Who knows, you may love it so much you decide to stay longer or move-in permanently!

Listing Title: AT&T Stadium,Globe Life,Texas Live!,Six Flags,UTA
Description:
BRAND NEW townhome! Near AT&T Stadium (1.1 miles), Globe Life Field (1.7 miles), Texas Live!(2.3 miles), Six Flags & Hurricane Harbor(3.1 miles)! 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, with incredible high-end finishes. Amenities include a private backyard, grill, games, fully equipped kitchen, 65" TV and master balcony. Walking distance to restaurants and UTA; 20 min. to DFW airport. Great space for families & small groups in a GREAT LOCATION and safe neighborhood! No Parties Allowed. No Smoking on property.

Location, Location, Location. We are located right in the heart of Arlington, minutes away from all the best attractions DFW has to offer and both airports(Dallas International and Dallas Love Field).

You get access to the entire place.

We are committed to provide all of our guests with an extraordinary experience. We strive to always be available to help if there is anything you may need. Simply use the AirBnb message platform for non-emergency messages or any questions you may have and we will respond promptly. We offer a simple, self check in process allowing for the privacy that most of our guests prefer. Rest assured our home is spacious, clean, and ready to be enjoyed by you. Let us know how we can make your stay a glowing 5-stars!

Quiet, family-friendly neighborhood. Convenient and centrally located, you are close to neighboring cities of Fort Worth and Dallas. Foodies will love the access to great food and restaurants. A quick walk or drive gets you to everything you need. Perfect home base for work or vacation, so make sure you check out some of the places to see/visit in our Guidebook. We hope you enjoy your stay in Arlington!

Parking should not be an issue with a 2 car tandum garage,  driveway and street parking available.

Spa services are available upon request. Spa services include massage,  facials, and nails. Neurotris beauty treatments will be coming soon. Please reach out to us directly for pricing.

The large private fenced-in backyard has a patio deck and a new covered stamp-concrete patio area with picnic table and zero-gravity loungers!

Guest have access to entire apartment

Only a 15 minute drive to DFW International Airport.

We take special care in cleaning and sanitizing. All linens, comforters, and throw blankets are thoroughly washed after every guest. Listing Title: ★5 Minute Walk! AT&T Cowboys and Rangers Stadium!★
Description:
The house is 3 easy walking blocks to the AT&T Cowboys Stadium, and a short walk to the Texas Rangers Globe Life Park, less than a mile drive to Six Flags and Hurricane Harbor! There are shopping malls, strip & outlet malls, & any type of restaurant & bar you could want within 15 mins. There is a short walk to Walmart, Walgreens, and Lincoln Square shopping & dining center. You are 20 min. from downtown Dallas to the east, and 20 min. from downtown Ft. Worth.

Why stay in a hotel when you can relax in an entire house? Comfortable and cozy, it’s your home away from home! As a guest you will have access to the entire house – a 3 Bedroom, 1 Bath, newly remodeled in 2016, and fully furnished with central heat and air conditioning. The home has nice furniture and décor, new flooring, bathroom and kitchen remodeled, everything is new throughout!

There are two TV's with Spectrum Cable TV and 300mbit Fiber Internet. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms and the living room, and the list goes on and on. The kitchen has everything you need for cooking and baking, refrigerator/freezer with ice maker and water dispenser, and a dishwasher. Full size washer and dryer. All bedroom linens are provided and are high quality and there is plenty of closet space.

The front bedroom has a pillow-top queen size bed, TV, and closet. The second bedroom has a pillow-top King size bed with closet. The third bedroom has two queen size pillow top beds. The living room has a sofa that can sleep a smaller person very comfortably. All linen, bedding, and mattresses are new and very clean. The house sleeps 8 comfortably.

The large private fenced-in backyard has a grill, new patio and table and chairs. There is ample driveway parking for up to 3 cars.

The house rents on average monthly from $2100 to $3000. Please contact me and I will happily work with you on monthly rentals. Please contact me with an inquiry if pricing seems off. Absolutely no parties allowed.

This renovated house is an absolute must-stay for your trip to Arlington and DFW areas. Whether you are visiting Arlington for entertainments, business trips, or gathering with friends and family, this house has it all at the affordable price.

-Coffeemaker with complimentary coffee, sugar and cream.

 -2 newly-renovated bathrooms with stand up and bathtub showers.  Plenty of towels for you and your party.
- Shampoo/conditioner, shower gel, hand soap, dish soap provided
-Use of onsite large washer and dryer with detergent convenient for sport events.
- Private and spacious patio for outdoor dining and seating area for your whole group to enjoy morning cup of coffee or evening glass of wine.
-Games, books available for your enjoyment

Self check-in available with door code.

We respect your absolute privacy; however we are only 10 minutes away if you would need any assistance during your stay.

Stay for 30+ nights (minimum nights and rates are FIRM) where you’ll have the entire apartment all to yourself at Wimbledon Oaks Apartment Homes. The apartment has beautiful finishes and comes fully outfitted with kitchen, bedroom, & bathroom essentials. Please note, the furnishings & room details WILL VARY as the unit is set up for you upon booking. We are an experienced professional hospitality company that works directly with the property to transform vacant units into your home away from home.

We take the health and safety of guests seriously. Between each stay, the apartment is thoroughly cleaned and sanitized following guidance from the CDC. Cleaners wear protective garments (e.g., mask, gloves) and wipe surfaces, cabinet handles, door knobs, etc. with cleaning solutions that follow CDC guidance. All linens, dishware, glassware and silverware are also washed between stays. Cleaning products and tools are provided so you can clean and sanitize as well.

We require Hosts and Guests to wear masks during any in-person interaction.

You’ll be staying in your own 1050 square-foot,  fully-furnished apartment including WiFi, smart TV, and all utilities (cable TV available by inquiry for additional cost). The floor plan provides an open living space with a fully-equipped kitchen, living room, and bathroom. The apartment is set up just for guests so it can truly feel like your home during your stay and there’s plenty of space to set up your laptop or stretch out on the couch.

You’ll have the apartment completely to yourself and can access building amenities (public health guidance permitting) that are included in your reservation (e.g., if parking is not purchased, parking access will not be granted).

Who knows, you may love it so much you decide to stay longer or move-in permanently!

Listing Title: Private entrance, sparkling clean, prime location
Description:
Prime location in Arlington with lots of privacy!

Just off I20 & Hwy 287, 5 minutes to loop 820, 20 minutes to AT&T Stadium and Globe Life Park. Access to shopping, food, and every convenience just minutes away.

Private entrance and parking in the driveway. Full private bathroom,  microwave, refrigerator, and coffee maker in the room. Owners primarily live on the second floor, so guests will have full privacy and quiet. 

Long term guests will also have access to washer and dryer if needed.

Absolutely no smoking or vaping.
We do have a young little dog. He's very friendly and you will likely not even see him, but you may occasionally hear the pitter patter of little feet. He's otherwise pretty quiet.

The room is completely locked off from the rest of the house so you will have lots of privacy. Guests will not have access to the kitchen, but the room has its own microwave, refrigerator, and coffee maker. Long term guests may have access to the washer and dryer if needed.

Guests are welcome to sit on the patio in the chairs right by the room. The deck and fire pit are not available for guest use.

I keep to myself and will give you full privacy, but I am available if you need something.

Quiet, safe neighborhood with great highway access.

The location is close to everything! Lots of places to eat and shop within minutes of your room.

the smoke alarm is not inside the actual room, it is just on the other side of the interior door

Smoking and vaping not allowed

Listing Title: WALK TO STADIUMS | FAMILY | GAME ROOM | HOT TUB
Description:
Arlington Funcation House is perfect for families, couple staycations, and business travelers that desire top quality accommodations. The house is well-appointed with everything you will need for a memorable enjoyable stay. Prime walking location for sporting or stadium events, Globe Life Field, AT&T, Texas Live, Esports Stadium, Arlington Convention Center. Short drive to Six Flags and Downtown Arlington. Hot Tub, Game Room, Putting Green, Luxury Accommodations.

Have questions or are ready to book? Message us. We are happy to help and will reply right away.

Enjoy time together with friends and family in our spacious living room with comfortable seating for everyone. Enjoy a movie night on one of our 7 Smart TVs.

Gather for a great meal at your home away from home. Our chef’s kitchen is fully equipped with quality cookware and everything you will need for a sit-down dinner. The kitchen and dining room have ample seating for your group to enjoy time together. Like to cook outdoors? Try our Weber gas grill.

Get your competitive game on in our unique mural surrounded game room featuring shuffleboard, PacMan and a foosball game table. Play board games or catch a movie on the 65-inch game room TV.  Become the star of your group with your singing skills or jam out with the karaoke machine sound system.

You will get a good night’s sleep on our comfortable Sealy Professional Hospitality mattresses and luxury super soft linens.  If you are a night owl or want to get away, all bedrooms have smart TVs with free local channels, free digital channels or you can stream your favorites movies on Netflix, Hulu, and Prime using your own account.

When the weather is nice, enjoy relaxing on the shaded back porch on our comfy outdoor lounge furniture and enjoy the view of the magnolia trees or play some mini golf on the private backyard putting green. Kids and adults of all ages can enjoy a game of mini golf.

Listing Title: Large and Private Stylish Downtown Apartment
Description:
Located just 1.3 miles from AT&T Stadium this 850 square foot stylish downtown apartment is newly remodeled and has a beautifully decorated interior. Huge bathroom; living area; private entrance and outdoor space; new appliances; fast high speed Internet; walking distance from entertainment and restaurants; less than 20 minutes drive from the DFW Airport. Perfectly suited for a very relaxing stay for one person or a couple. Pet friendly space; not suitable for people with pet allergies.

The apartment is in an established residential area in downtown Arlington within blocks of entertainment, restaurants, and coffee shops— all within walking distance. It is very private, with its own outdoor space and carport. Perfect for a relaxing break for one person or a couple.

Covered porch, yard, carport.

I am available to answer questions by phone, text, or messages though the Airbnb app. I generally give people space to enjoy their stay, but I’m also very happy to answer questions and provide advice on the area as needed.

This is a very walkable neighborhood. We are two blocks from the campus of the University of Texas at Arlington, College Park Center (for basketball and other live events), three Starbucks, and four independent coffee shops. The Levitt Pavilion is two blocks away also, with a packed calendar of free outdoor music events. You can walk to many restaurants and bars from here. Dallas and Fort Worth are 25 minutes drive in opposite directions, and DFW airport is 20 minutes away. The Cowboys stadium is a little over a mile. The new Rangers stadium is about two miles. And Six Flags is two and a half miles. This is a perfect base for exploring it all, and then coming home for a stroll to dinner.

Arlington does not have public transport so a car is ideal for exploring further afield than downtown. The city has its own ride service- Via. You can walk to all the necessary locations—like restaurants and a seven eleven— from the apartment.

The apartment is set up just for guests so it can truly feel like your home during your stay and there’s plenty of space to set up your laptop or stretch out on the couch.

You’ll have the apartment completely to yourself and can access building amenities (public health guidance permitting) that are included in your reservation (e.g., if parking is not purchased, parking access will not be granted).

Listing Title: Ideal  AT&T stadium  location & Vibrant Entire Apt
Description:
Beautiful and Bright  1 bedroom apt in the ♥ of Arlington 
Easy and fast access to the freeway between 2 major cities Dallas & Fort Worth
 ➤ 7 min Global Life / Cowboys Stadium
➤ 12 min DFW airport 
➤20 min to Dallas Downtown 
➤ 22 min to Fort Worth Downtown 
 

Perfect for students, visitors, business travelers, and couples.  
También hablamos español!

The space has been thoughtfully designed to stimulate positivity and relaxation. 

Private room with a  brand-new memory foam queen  bed and 22" Queen Comfort High Rise Airbed Mattress with Built-In Pump
☛ Fully Equipped kitchen
☛ Laundry amenities in the apartment washer & dryer  
☛ Office desk & chair 
☛ Cute small patio balcony 

Amenities include: 
☛ Coffee Machine (Regular & Decaf )  & French Press  and Variety of tea 
☛ Smart TV with Netflix  in the living room. 
☛  Extra blankets and pillows for maximum coziness are available upon request. 
☛ Colored pencils and Color Me Stress-Free or Color Me Calm coloring books for an artistic outlet to find relaxation and meditation or to unplug and rewind 
☛ Paper maps and guides for the city of Dallas & Fort Worth Metroplex , Texas.

We want you to make yourselves at home.

Note: Covid-19 safety measure are in place. My unit is thoroughly cleaned before and after each stay, sanitized throughout the entire unit.

Feel like home at the apartment any issues or problems please contact me via text , airbnb , or call .

LEASING OFFICE
DO NOT enter the leasing office or talk to the property management staff for any reason. We have a mutual agreement with the complex that all our guests communicate ONLY through the Airbnb platform. From there, our team can directly communicate with the complex on your behalf.  Any violation of this agreement will lead to an immediate termination of your reservation. If we receive any lease violations (smoking, noise complaints, trash, etc.), you will be charged with a $200 fine

I'm available through the Airbnb app 
Telegram ,  Viber , Whatsapp
